      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question, i just got a prescription for clarithromycin for a sinus infection but im also on simvastatin for my cholesterol. is it cool to take both at the same time or do i need to skip my statin while i take the antibiotics?",
      "source": "evaluator"
